name: Vintage
description: This was posted on Twitter. I made the first one when copy minting was rampant on @hicetnunc and @jjjjjjjjjjohn was a particular target. The creator ID system was not in place and verification had to be done on a second platform. After the 1st one "FAKE" I discovered I really liked playing in the format. I post this not as art but just as a document from April 2021.
